{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回 青出于蓝\n\n本章讲述了小鱼儿在恶人谷中的日常。他戏弄新来的巴蜀东，骗走了他的缅铁软刀。巴蜀东在谷中遇到了老朋友宋三（闷雷刀），得知小鱼儿在谷中称霸，连各位恶人都惧怕他三分。宋三透露自己的断臂与小鱼儿入谷有关，但话未说完就被阴九幽杀害。屠娇娇和李大嘴随后现身，三位恶人前往杜杀处商议，决定将小鱼儿赶出恶人谷。与此同时，小鱼儿来到万春流处，两人谈及燕南天的病情。小鱼儿回忆五年前神秘黑衣人告知他身世的秘密，推断此人是女性，武功高强，与移花宫有仇。最后屠娇娇来找小鱼儿，章节在悬念中结束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也算坏事吗？……嘿，这种坏事简直只有赶骡车的粗汉才会做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我来得如此匆忙，哪有什么稀奇之物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若没有东西，就露两手成名的绝技给我瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还……还有什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也是规矩？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这也是规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我从未听过‘恶人谷’有这样的规矩。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东又怔住了，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那么这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我的规矩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那边的是巴二弟么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东瞧了两眼，大喜呼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闷雷刀宋三哥，你！你果然在这里！可找死小弟了……小弟此番正是投奔三哥来的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东瞧见他，脸色立刻又变了，恨声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宋三哥，这小鬼……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东又惊又奇，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三哥为何如此怕他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东惊得目瞪口呆，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小鬼有如此厉害？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东讷讷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能相信……小弟简直不能相信。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这正是他入谷那日断去的，十四年，已有十四年了。燕南天那么厉害的身手，若非我当机立断，只怕已活不到今日。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shu_dong",
      "speaker_name": "巴蜀东失声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南天？这小鬼是燕南天的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽龇牙一笑，阴森森",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在本谷之中，谁也不准提起小鱼儿和姓燕的事，你忘了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我还未来得及向他说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三身子直往后退，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阴老九现在怎地也慈悲起来了，这厮方才说这一句话，你已该将他宰了的，为何到现在还不动手？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正要留给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要瞧瞧你那销魂掌可有进步？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不知道，我怎会知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "突听小鱼儿的笑声远远传了过来，笑着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "醋坛子，皱鼻子，娶个老婆生儿子，儿子儿子没鼻子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既在老西那里，想必不会听到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒可是也要去杜老大处？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是要去的，哈哈儿突然要咱们聚在一起，不知又要搞什么鬼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "人都已来齐了，哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，哈哈，咱们许久未曾如此热闹了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最恨的就是热闹，你将我找来，若没话说，我……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你找咱们来，莫非为了那小鱼儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，还是小屠聪明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为了那小鬼？为那小鬼有什么好谈的，你们一个教他杀人，一个教他害人，一个教他哭，一个教他笑……好了，他现在不是全学会了么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为全学会了，所以我才请各位来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为啥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿叹了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我受不了啦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴苦着脸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁受得了谁是孙子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今这位小太爷，要来就来，要走就走，要吃就吃，要喝就喝，谁也不敢惹他，惹了他就倒楣，‘恶人谷’可真受够了他了，这几个月来，至少有三十个人向我诉苦，每人至少诉过八次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们害人，多少还有个目的，这小鬼害人却只是为了好玩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们本来不就正希望他如此么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们本来希望他害的是别人呀，谁知这小鬼竟是六亲不认，见人就害……这其中恐怕只有小屠舒服些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我舒服……我舒服个屁，我那几手，这小鬼简直全学会了，而且简直学得比我自己还地道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜老大怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀默然半晌，终于缓缓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻若将他与我关在一个屋子里，那活着出来的人，必定是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇叹了口气，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了，现在好了，‘恶人谷’都已受不了他，何况别人，现在只怕已是请他出去的时候……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴赶紧截口",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是极是极，他害咱们已害够了，正该让他去害害别人了，现在幸好咱们联手还能制他，等到一日，若是咱们加起来也制不住他时，就完蛋了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "阴九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要送他走越快越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_sha",
      "speaker_name": "杜杀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是今朝！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，江湖中的各位朋友们……黑道的朋友们，白道的朋友们，山上的朋友们，水里的朋友们，你们受罪的日子已到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "万春流将七种药草放在瓦罐里熬，此刻正在观察着药汁的变化，瞧见小鱼儿进来，将垂下眼皮一抬，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日有何收获？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刀在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送给醋坛子老西了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流以筷子搅动着药汁，浓浓的水雾，使他的脸看来仿佛有些神秘，他",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那小箱子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你辛苦弄来，为何要送人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若没有这些呆子，怎显得你我之快乐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿起这药罐，随我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这五年来，竟无丝毫变化，我已几乎将所有的药都试遍了，我……我累得很。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿呆呆地出了半天神，突然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我今天听见有人提起燕伯伯的名字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流动容",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人！说话的人已死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿点头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道，万叔叔冒了生命的危险来救燕伯伯，我……我难道不感激，别人就算砍下我脑袋，我也不会说一个字的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流叹息",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说实话，我本不敢相信你的，哪知你虽然生长在这环境中，却还没有失去良心，还是个好孩子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流竟也展颜一笑，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但五年前那天晚上，你突然跑来对我说，你已知道‘药罐子’叔叔是什么人，你已知道这秘密时．我可当真吓了一跳。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流默然半晌，笑着又皱眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再想想，对你说出这秘密的人，究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿想了想",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那天晚上，我是睡在杜杀外面的屋子里，半夜里，我突然觉得身子竟似被人抱了起来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喊也喊不出，何况，那时我还以为是杜杀又不知在用什么花样对付我，根本没想到是别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只觉那人身法快得简直骇人，我躺在他怀里，就像是腾云驾雾似的，片刻间，就远远离开了‘恶人谷’。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时你真的不怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老虎我都不怕，怎会怕人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人将我放到地上，就问我：‘你姓什么？’我说：‘不知道。’那人就骂我简直和畜生一样，连姓什么都不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后，他就告诉你你姓江？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，他还说我爹爹叫江枫，是被‘移花宫’中的人害死的，他叫我千万莫忘了这仇恨，长大了一定要找‘移花宫’的人复仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他真的没有提起‘江琴’这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，你燕伯伯到‘恶人谷’来，本是为的要找个叫‘江琴’的人，为的也正是要代你爹爹报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许江琴也是我仇人之一。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那天晚上很黑，我只瞧见他穿着一件黑袍子，头上也戴着个黑布罩，两只眼睛，又亮又大，又怕人……这双眼睛我到现在还忘不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后你再见到这双眼睛还能认得么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定认得的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这双眼睛不是谷中的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝不是，谷中无论是谁的眼睛，都没有这双眼睛那么亮，屠娇娇的眼睛虽也亮，但和他一比，简直就是睁眼瞎子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想必是个武功很高的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是自然，江湖中能随意进出‘恶人谷’的人，除了你燕伯伯外，我简直想不出还有几个？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个都没有了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有的就是‘移花宫’中大小两位宫主，但这人既然要你找‘移花宫’中的人报仇，又怎会是这两位宫主？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿突然拍手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，我想起来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人是女的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流动容",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，她虽然蒙着脸，而且故意将说话的声音扮得很粗，但看她有时的举动，却必定是个女的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么举动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "比如……她头上虽然戴着布罩，但在无意中却还不时去摸头发，还有，她虽然将我抱在怀里，但总是不让我碰到她的胸……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但总是有个人的，第一，这人认得我爹爹，也认得燕伯伯，第二，这人对我爹爹死的原因知道得很清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想必如此！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第三，这人不但知道我家的仇恨，而且，还很关心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但我要去找她，第一先得出这‘恶人谷’，我……我什么时候才能走出去呢？他们什么时候才会放我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "万神医，小鱼儿可是在这里么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_chun_liu",
      "speaker_name": "万春流变色",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "屠娇娇来找你了，快出去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    }
